    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "\n",
        "customers['SignupDate'] = pd.to_datetime(customers['SignupDate'])\n",
        "transactions['TransactionDate'] = pd.to_datetime(transactions['TransactionDate'])\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "merged_data = transactions.merge(customers, on=\"CustomerID\").merge(products, on=\"ProductID\")\n",
        "print(merged_data.head())\n"
      ],

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Calculate revenue by category\n",
        "category_revenue = merged_data.groupby('Category')['TotalValue'].sum().sort_values(ascending=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Plot revenue by category\n",
        "category_revenue.plot(kind='bar', figsize=(10, 6), title='Revenue by Product Category', color='skyblue')\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"Total Revenue (USD)\")\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"Product Category\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n"
      ],

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "\n",
        "merged_data['YearMonth'] = merged_data['TransactionDate'].dt.to_period('M')\n",
        "\n",
        "monthly_revenue = merged_data.groupby('YearMonth')['TotalValue'].sum()\n",
        "\n",
        "monthly_revenue.plot(kind='line', figsize=(12, 6), marker='o', title='Monthly Revenue Trend', color='green')\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"Total Revenue (USD)\")\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"Year-Month\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n"
      ],
